title: Eagan girls to defend their state crown after defeating Burnsville
text: Eagan to defend its Class 2A state title after defeating Burnsville 10/21/2015, 11:30am CDT By Trevor Squire, Sport Ngin Taylor Kenealy scored twice to help send the reigning state champion Wildcats back to the state tournament. Eagan celebrates after Anni Christenson's goal early in the first half of the Wildcats matchup with Burnsville in the Class 2A, Section 3 championship on Oct. 21. Eagan won 4-0.
